 stereo to B-format panning, horizontal rotator, square, hexagon and cube
 decoders.

Package: ambdec
Description-md5: 55a5b8c43a1bddf956c4e69ea0fddf88
Description-en_GB: Ambisonic decoder for first and second order
 AmbDec is an Ambisonics decoder for up to 36 speakers. It can be used for both horizontal and full 3-D systems of first, second and third order. The decoding matrices are fully user-configurable. AmbDec has some advanced features not found on most decoders:
  * Dual frequency band operation.
  * Speaker distance compensation.
  * Near-field effect compensation.
 .
 All three features can be selectively enabled or disabled in the
 configuration.

Package: amber
Description-md5: cbfffa4666c07558976428469cbfdea0
Description-en_GB: Elegant HTML templating engine for Go, inspired from HAML and Jade (CLI tool)
 Amber is an elegant HTML templating engine for the Go Programming
 Language. It is inspired from HAML and Jade.
 .
 This package provides the /usr/bin/amberc command-line tool.

Package: amide
