Package: an
Description-md5: c3a81b8c3754d57849b4791d04d63fde
Description-en_GB: very fast anagram generator
 Generates anagrams for a phrase supplied by the user, the words used in
 the anagram are taken from a specified dictionary which should contain one
 word per line (default:/usr/share/dict/words). It understands accented
