Package: autobahn-cpp-dev
Description-md5: 9db91b707d3e8ed92524b84df9da4e5c
Description-en_GB: WAMP in C++ for Boost/Asio - development headers
 Autobahn|Cpp provides an implementation of the WebSocket and Web
