Description-md5: 4aec1b3d39600b35a6836d343a1c5afc
Description-en_GB: automatic configure script builder (Thomas Dickey's version)
 This hacked version of autoconf is required to bootstrap ncurses and some
 other packages maintained upstream by Thomas Dickey. It should not be used
 for other purposes.

