 distributed through different networks and connected via NAT. In most of
 cases you may just install miredo, gogoc or any other tunnel broker's
 software and these computers will be available via IPv6 addresses.
 BOSixNet includes the collection of tools for automatic updating the list
 of such hosts.
 .
