Package: ccls
Description-md5: a0041ae63c0c8de35e4287f98d9d0b4e
Description-en_GB: C/C++/ObjC language server
 This originates from cquery, and is a server implementing Language Server
 Protocol for C/C++/Objective-C. It supports:
 .
  * code completion (with both signature help and snippets)
  * definition/references, and other cross references
  * cross reference extensions:
