Package: chromimpute
Description-md5: e3e50d55b8034f014bbadcc1b2d6ff71
Description-en_GB: Large-scale systematic epigenome imputation
 ChromImpute takes an existing compendium of epigenomic data and uses it to
 predict signal tracks for mark-sample combinations not experimentally
 mapped or to generate a potentially more robust version of data sets that
 have been mapped experimentally. ChromImpute bases its predictions on
 features from signal tracks of other marks that have been mapped in the
 target sample and the target mark in other samples with these features
 combined using an ensemble of regression trees.

