Description-en_GB: protein sequence conservation scoring tool
 This package provides score_conservation(1), a tool to score protein
 sequence conservation.
 .
 The following conservation scoring methods are implemented:
  * sum of pairs
  * weighted sum of pairs
  * Shannon entropy
  * Shannon entropy with property groupings (Mirny and Shakhnovich 1995,
