 Debian Astro is a "Debian Pure Blend" with the aim to develop a Debian
 based operating system that fits the requirements of both professional and
 hobby astronomers. It integrates a large number of software packages
 covering telescope control, data reduction, presentation and other fields.
 .
 This package contains the Logo of the Debian Astronomy Pure Blend in
