Description-md5: 0110fd81fff2ee9c49502b34005216c8
Description-en_GB: DebiChem Molecular Ab Initio Calculations
 This metapackage will install packages doing molecular ab initio
 calculations which might be useful for chemists.

Package: debichem-molecular-dynamics
Description-md5: d81e92bf0a50287febc5485be27e92a3
Description-en_GB: DebiChem Molecular Dynamics
 This metapackage will install Molecular Dynamics packages which might be
