 expectations through a learning process. In terms of types of agents,
 models solved by Dynare can incorporate consumers, productive firms,
 governments, monetary authorities, investors and financial intermediaries.
 Some degree of heterogeneity can be achieved by including several distinct
 classes of agents in each of the aforementioned agent categories.
 .
 Dynare offers a user-friendly and intuitive way of describing these
 models. It is able to perform simulations of the model given a calibration
 of the model parameters and is also able to estimate these parameters
