 EDFbrowser is a viewer for medical timeseries storage files containing
 data such as EEG, EMG, and ECG signals.  It supports EDF(+) and BDF(+)
 file formats. Apart from viewing the files, it also supports some editing
 operations and can convert the biomedical files to other formats.

