Description-en_GB: EiskaltDC++ daemon
 This package installs only EiskaltDC++ daemon (without any GUI). Support
 of control via JSON-RPC is enabled. Look at EiskaltDC++ CLI and Web UI
 programs for controlling it.
 .
 EiskaltDC++ Qt and GTK+ UI may be used for configuring of EiskaltDC++
 daemon (they use the same settings from core library), but they should not
 be launched simultaneously.
 .
