Package: electronics-pcb
Description-md5: 824ae29f83415e8a6af002b2a7f5ee0b
Description-en_GB: Debian packages for PCB development
 This metapackage will install Debian packages useful for the development
 of printed circuit boards.

Package: electronics-radio-dev
Description-md5: 2ecf051d2ae8fc3d7394da63eadd0bd3
Description-en_GB: Packages for design of circuits at radio frequencies
 This metapackage will install Debian packages for design at radio/
