Package: elpa-clojure-mode-extra-font-locking
Description-md5: 9db33411d58e2cd61eb076f78cbf48b3
Description-en_GB: extra font-locking for clojure-mode
 Provides additional font-locking (syntax highlighting) for clojure-mode.
