Package: elpa-ghub
Description-md5: 5379c42710503d1b745d864bc172eecd
Description-en_GB: minuscule client for the Github API
 A minuscule client for the Github API.
 .
 This library just provides the HTTP verbs. Instead of wrapping every
 resource, https://developer.github.com/v3 is recommended. Due to the lack
 of doc-strings, it's also recommended having a quick look at the source,
