 commit message for the current line. This is useful when you want to know
 why this line was changed. This uses the git-blame tool internally.

Package: elpa-git-modes
Description-md5: 3ef0d7edd415c6d91ac2bf458039e00e
Description-en_GB: major modes for editing Git configuration files
 This package provides several major modes for editing Git configuration
 files. The modes are:
 .
  * gitattributes-mode
  * gitconfig-mode
  * gitignore-mode
 .
