 modes' causes all three libraries to be loaded, but you could also load
 the libraries individually.

Package: elpa-git-timemachine
Description-md5: 29d5bb2504be04bc7d21308ac1491bd5
Description-en_GB: walk through git revisions of a file
 Emacs mode that helps to walk through git revisions of a file. It can be
 used to browse historic versions of a file with p (previous) and n (next)
 keys. Also one can jump to a particular revision, copy abbreviate or full
 hash of the current revision.

Package: elpa-gitattributes-mode
Description-md5: 7b7e1f9021f3637c6a7d166f722779af
