Package: elpa-lbdb
Description-md5: c13e47ac6d806bb155a7b77d17830059
Description-en_GB: Little Brother's DataBase Emacs extensions
 This package is an extension of the lbdb package, which contains ldbd.el,
 an Emacs interface to the Little Brother's Datebase lbdb.
 .
