 converter. It also includes fbgs, a Postscript and PDF viewer.

Package: fbless
Description-md5: 4f53417fea7776e9aebc7edf16853442
Description-en_GB: terminal fiction book reader
 Fbreader is ncurses fiction book (.fb2) reader with following features:
 .
  * customisable colour themes
