Description-en_GB: Catalan female speaker for festival, 16kHz HTS
 This is a Catalan female HTS voice for festival that uses 16kHz samples.
 Using festival, this package allows one to transform written text to
 speech spoken with a high quality female voice.
 .
 This voice was generated with 10 hours of recordings at Universitat
 Politècnica de Catalunya.

