 FFLAS-FFPACK consists in the creation of a set of routines, giving the
 same tools as a set of classical Basic Linear Algebra Subroutines, but
 working over finite fields. In the same way, some other routines of higher
 level (such as the one in LAPACK) are also produced.

Package: fflas-ffpack-common
Description-md5: f4da176092e0c009ac9f62f9a5bf6277
Description-en_GB: Finite field linear algebra subroutines/package - common files
 FFLAS-FFPACK consists in the creation of a set of routines, giving the
