Description-en_GB: Fast Library for Approximate Nearest Neighbors - documentation
 FLANN is a library for performing fast approximate nearest neighbor
 searches in high dimensional spaces. It contains a collection of
 algorithms found to work best for nearest neighbor search and a system for
 automatically choosing the best algorithm and optimum parameters depending
 on the dataset.
 .
 This package contains the documentation for FLANN.

