 the address of a variable in a running process. This can be used for the
 analysis or modification of a hostile process on a compromised machine,
 for reverse engineering, or as a "pokefinder" to cheat at video games.
 .
 GameConqueror provides a CheatEngine-alike user-friendly interface with
 more features than scanmem.

