Description-md5: 5ba7f28cfbbd6982f3d9a31469f11e55
Description-en_GB: Lemonldap::NG Web-SSO system documentation
 Lemonldap::NG is a complete Web-SSO system that can run with reverse-
 proxies or directly on application webservers. It can be used in
 conjunction with OpenID-Connect, CAS and SAML systems as identity or
 service provider. It can also be used as proxy between those federation
 systems.
 .
 It manages both authentication and authorization and provides headers for
 accounting. So you can have a full AAA protection. Authorizations are
 built by associating a regular expression and a rule. Regular expression
 is applied on the requested URL and the rule calculates if the user is
 authorized.
 .
